91 5. Once grants are approved by the solid waste management district, the district shall
92 submit to the department the appropriate forms associated with the grant application and any
93 supporting information to verify that appropriate public notice procedures were followed, that
94 grant proposals were reviewed and ranked by the district, and that only eligible costs as set
95 forth in regulations are to be funded. Within thirty days, the department shall review the grant
96 application. If the department finds any deficiencies, or needs more information in order to
